name: Cozy 1BR apartment
neighborhood_overview:
In quiet historic Fort Hill, 7-10 min walk to orange line Jackson sq,
Roxbury Crossing, minutes to downtown Boston.
description:
Cozy garden level one bedroom apartment with modern kitchen, bath. Close to orange line T, longwood medical/BU medical area and all universities.

The space
Guest can access the kitchen/bedroom/bath within the unit,
through the kitchen door connects to basement section washer/dryer.
The stove oven doesn't work, there's a table top oven/toaster.
Host lives nearby not in the same building.
The street is a small one way street with free on street parking no
permit required.

Guest access
Kitchen, washer dryer on site. Wifi.
